{"tid":926313,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"指會敗陣新東補選　梁國雄：虛位以待　服從民主派差遣","createTime":"2018-12-03T10:59:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T05:52:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e1607508b6a9112deee39320bfcfcb8583bf3c73","tid":926313,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T10:59:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/政情/265744/被指會敗陣新東補選-梁國雄-虛位以待-服從民主派差遣\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85%2F265744%2F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%9C%83%E6%95%97%E9%99%A3%E6%96%B0%E6%9D%B1%E8%A3%9C%E9%81%B8-%E6%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%84-%E8%99%9B%E4%BD%8D%E4%BB%A5%E5%BE%85-%E6%9C%8D%E5%BE%9E%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E5%B7%AE%E9%81%A3&d=HDF4iqn3TsE2X21HJ8eDoJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=a2e60ac7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/政情/265744/被指會敗陣新東補選-梁國雄-虛位以待-服從民主派差遣</a><br />\n<br />\n指會敗陣新東補選　梁國雄：虛位以待　服從民主派差遣<br />\n<br />\n政情<br />\n<br />\n撰文：莊恭南<br />\n<br />\n2018-12-01 00:04<br />\n<br />\n最後更新日期：2018-12-01 14:04<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2158369/org/e54822cbf8acef933380b04570e769f1.jpg/4RZ5kVVqtW8Qs6zz1Juay6msvFIf63Zb7BcNzOwXDcw?v=w1120r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2158369%2Forg%2Fe54822cbf8acef933380b04570e769f1.jpg%2F4RZ5kVVqtW8Qs6zz1Juay6msvFIf63Zb7BcNzOwXDcw%3Fv%3Dw1120r16_9&h=7669617c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n社會民主連線今日（30日）舉辦週年籌款晚宴，筵開66席。民主派各黨包括參選村代表面臨DQ的議會陣線朱凱迪，以及剛在九龍西補選飲恨的工黨李卓人等都有出席。<br />\n<br />\n早前有報道指，泛民中有人擔心社民連前立法會議員、被DQ的梁國雄若代表陣營出戰新東補選，或會敗選，建議派新人出戰。梁國雄在晚宴致詞時作出回應，指各DQ議員之中，自己是「守尾門」，又形容新東補選是「虛位以待」，他會「服從民主派的差遣」：我梁國雄贏唔贏到唔重要，最緊要係香港人要贏。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2158370/org/7f3d2d05afa9387e70ae33feff0cd618.jpg/TFpjStRVmFMLm-zN6lPzqphhjKz2WwNSNMZkHjTGZB4?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2158370%2Forg%2F7f3d2d05afa9387e70ae33feff0cd618.jpg%2FTFpjStRVmFMLm-zN6lPzqphhjKz2WwNSNMZkHjTGZB4%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=598c5f46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉小麗和李卓人亦有到場支持。（莊恭南攝）<br />\n<br />\n社民連主席吳文遠致詞時表示， 上周日九西補選泛民敗選，相信許多同路人心情至今仍未恢復，但他鼓勵眾人，「社民連每年都差不多滅黨，但至今仍然能屹立」，呼籲友好及支持者不需要灰心，「只要謹記心中擁有的價值 ，我們就永遠不會輸」，又寄語民主派在抗爭路上都要守望相助 。演說贏得台下掌聲雷動。<br />\n<br />\n梁國雄向台下表示，「中共統治巔峰已過」，民主運動隨後就會贏，又點名著晚宴嘉賓、佔中九子之一的「李永達你唔好傻笑」，令台下隨即響起一陣笑聲。梁國雄祝酒說：「為所有被中共壓迫的政治犯和香港未來乾杯。」眾人就以「香港人，打不死」回應。<br />\n<br />\n李卓人、劉小麗、佔中九子等亦相繼上台發言。劉小麗指，雖然暫時未放下敗選的難過，稱民主運動確實受到創傷，但認為今次補選民主派「用盡辦法打一場仗，雖然結果是輸，但大家一齊贏回了民主派對民主運動的投入。」<br />\n<br />\n晚宴又設義賣籌款環節，款額雖不如建制派般多，但在人民力量陳志全與「阿牛」曾健成擔任拍賣官下氣氛依然熱烈。一幅「千磨萬擊還勁堅」字畫，以千元起拍，范國威、郭家麒、毛孟靜等競相出價，令價格從1.4萬元、1.9萬元、再到2萬元不斷飆升，最終，有份為佔中九子案辯護的人權律師潘熙等一眾法律界人士合力以2.6萬元奪標。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2158373/org/69054b3499cea8500ad5dffe6a19e10f.jpg/wZ14epNYRuwHJYoendtkAooB3PDEdpStR9uEw0fbhMM?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2158373%2Forg%2F69054b3499cea8500ad5dffe6a19e10f.jpg%2FwZ14epNYRuwHJYoendtkAooB3PDEdpStR9uEw0fbhMM%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=fd32fe64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳淑莊未完成編織的頸巾，最終以1.8萬元被網台節目主持人桑普投得。（莊恭南攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2158371/org/8bab228fd21542ffc61d409188342403.jpg/HQ5VYs9YRWb-I7VyKp4Z23GkNy28GZf9ardvwWq3b8E?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2158371%2Forg%2F8bab228fd21542ffc61d409188342403.jpg%2FHQ5VYs9YRWb-I7VyKp4Z23GkNy28GZf9ardvwWq3b8E%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=e3246a73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多個民主派政黨亦有「撐場」。（莊恭南攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2158372/org/13a751f1b4645c2e003dac6b556bb039.jpg/4Fb82y761AED-25_Lfk99uC6nMy6jpw8m-Zg1ZvmYNU?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2158372%2Forg%2F13a751f1b4645c2e003dac6b556bb039.jpg%2F4Fb82y761AED-25_Lfk99uC6nMy6jpw8m-Zg1ZvmYNU%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=15b33414&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人民力量陳志全與阿牛曾健成擔任拍賣官。（莊恭南攝）"},{"pid":"44bbf4f061570029f4eb400c7705498d89cc6d64","tid":926313,"uid":20522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T11:01:01.000Z","msg":"你有票？我唔要呀"},{"pid":"bf2420025ee73d9aebf339388844601bb27c7ad2","tid":926313,"uid":187076,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T11:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FBeNioW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFBeNioW.jpg&h=f4109e9e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b4a88e3d997c63ccdd48e7cc4b6cd852a4c0965d","tid":926313,"uid":197364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T13:30:19.000Z","msg":"收皮啦阿哥，回撚哂塘<br />\n<br />\n第一次見人激進到「服從安排」<br />\n<br />\n好心長毛回撚哂塘就收皮啦，正宗被權力腐化嘅撚人"},{"pid":"9e4f50a0e1c904c2326d08301ebfa59ffe9f5e40","tid":926313,"uid":8504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T13:32:35.000Z","msg":"教主講得啱 泛民係咁屌票 又唔撚拉大個政治光譜 吸番本土派既票 你選新東夠票先奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc7b08847527acd55640e72c7f7f46e0397860e","tid":926313,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T19:26:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">他會「服從民主派的差遣」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f53551ca2321faa13962d797a33567047d13de","tid":926313,"uid":224673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T19:36:53.000Z","msg":"見到泛民已作嘔"},{"pid":"4a55cdf955e6b4abe5228bf607b43ea87471e257","tid":926313,"uid":69924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e4f50a0e1c904c2326d08301ebfa59ffe9f5e40","tid":926313,"uid":8504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-